videos.headline: Young finds Bolden for TD on Alabama's opening drive

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One Play (Young finds Bolden for TD on Alabama's opening drive) 12/31/21 ESHEET

videos.headline: Robinson runs over defender on 4th-down run
videos.description: Brian Robinson Jr. picks up the first down by running over the defender.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One Play (Robinson runs over defender on 4th-down run) 12/31/21 ESHEET

videos.headline: Alabama gets unsportsmanlike penalty after throwing Cincinnati punter off pile
videos.description: Alabama muffs the punt and recovers it, but is moved back as Jaylen Moody gets a penalty for throwing the Cincinnati punter off the pile.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One Play (Alabama gets unsportsmanlike penalty after throwing Cincinnati punter off pile) 12/31/21 ESHEET

videos.headline: Young tosses it deep to Brooks for 44-yard TD
videos.description: Bryce Young goes up top to Ja'Corey Brooks, who reaches across the pylon for 44-yard touchdown.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One Play (Young tosses it deep to Brooks for 44-yard TD) 12/31/21 ESHEET

videos.headline: Anderson ends half in style with sack of Ridder
videos.description: Cincinnati tries for the Hail Mary to end the half, but Alabama's Will Anderson breaks through and gets the sack.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One Play (Anderson ends half in style with sack of Ridder) 12/31/21 ESHEET

videos.headline: Young sails one and Cincinnati picks it off
videos.description: Bryce Young sails a pass over the receiver's head and it's intercepted by Bryan Cook.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One Play (Young sails one and Cincinnati picks it off) 12/31/21 ESHEET

videos.headline: Cincinnati's Pace gets penalty for ripping Williams' helmet off
videos.description: Cincinnati's Deshawn Pace gets a penalty after tackling Jameson Williams and ripping his helmet off after the play.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One Play (Cincinnati's Pace gets penalty for ripping Williams' helmet off) 12/31/21 ESHEET

videos.headline: Young finds Latu over the middle for Alabama TD
videos.description: Bryce Young finds an open Cameron Latu for the 9-yard Alabama touchdown.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One Play (Young finds Latu over the middle for Alabama TD) 12/31/21 ESHEET

videos.headline: Ridder takes huge sack on 4th down
videos.description: Alabama's Brian Branch and Will Anderson Jr. get to Desmond Ridder for the sack, giving the ball back to the Crimson Tide in the fourth.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One Play (Ridder takes huge sack on 4th down) 12/31/21 ESHEET

videos.headline: Young's 3 TDs, Robinson Jr's strong ground game propels Bama to CFP Championship
videos.description: Bryce Young slings three touchdowns and Brian Robinson Jr. tallies 204 yards as Alabama cruises into the CFP title game.

tracking.trackingName: COM_NCF Highlight (Young’s 3 TDs, Robinson Jr’s strong ground game propels Bama to CFP Championship) 2021/12/31 ESHEET SOTFULL

videos.headline: Saban stresses that No. 1 Bama's job is not finished
videos.description: Although pleased with the overall performance of Alabama in a 27-6 dismantling of Cincinnati, Nick Saban has his eyes on a national championship.

videos.headline: Robinson Jr. says patience paid off with Bama record
videos.description: After rushing for 204 yards, the most in Alabama bowl game history, Brian Robinson Jr. says when the time came, "I was ready for it."

videos.headline: Robinson Jr., No. 1 Bama stiff-arm No. 4 Cincinnati
videos.description: Brian Robinson Jr. and the Crimson Tide run all over the Bearcats, 27-6, to advance to another National Championshp game.
